
Sample idsad configuration files

idsad.conf                 - default configuration file with lots of logging
idsad-signatures.conf      - sample signatures triggering on unusual activity
idsad-interactive.conf     - approve remote logins interactively using 
                             idsaguardtty or idsaguardgtk
idsad-simple.conf          - very simple logging rule

Additions 

httpd.conf                 - addition to apache to enable mod_idsa
inetd.conf                 - example of using idsatcpd, a tcp wrapper replacement
pam-example                - an example of using pam_idsa

Startup scripts

rc.idsa-full               - start all idsa services
rc.idsa-simple             - only start the main server and connection logger

Template files

*.in                       - source files, can be ignored
